    "description": "开放世界+俄罗斯方块=？<br>看完你就知道答案了。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >不止是俄罗斯方块</h2>在破壁世界中，每个小空间都是一次特殊的俄罗斯方块谜题。你需要发挥你的智慧打破三面墙，找出逃离黑暗的方式。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2055620/extras/994578a40358a7cd427959821cb3026a.avif?t=1665541470\" width=627 height=439 /></span><br><br>在破壁世界中，大部分的东西都可以被消除。每一次你进行破壁消除时，都会获得能量奖励，这是一种强大的能量，类似魔法值，是你释放强力法术的基础。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2055620/extras/7bf26e1c28dcd88a65b341cacd7f0389.poster.avif?t=1665541470\" width=640 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2055620/extras/7bf26e1c28dcd88a65b341cacd7f0389.webm?t=1665541470\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2055620/extras/7bf26e1c28dcd88a65b341cacd7f0389.mp4?t=1665541470\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >开放世界</h2>作为有诸多挑战关卡的游戏，我们摈弃了传统的关卡选择，你可以随时在不同个挑战中进行切换。是继续完成当前谜题还是换一个方向，选择其他的内容挑战，都有你自己决定。<br>这也为巨大谜题提供了有趣的选择。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2055620/extras/7f927e179dcd20e09661c58e345099f8.poster.avif?t=1665541470\" width=640 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2055620/extras/7f927e179dcd20e09661c58e345099f8.webm?t=1665541470\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2055620/extras/7f927e179dcd20e09661c58e345099f8.mp4?t=1665541470\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>伴随着房间谜题，也有很多野外空间，他们大多是迷人的绚丽场景。这里面是不是存在着什么秘密？<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2055620/extras/b162a958175c0d103d4b3d6db6694097.avif?t=1665541470\" width=800 height=440 /></span><br><br>相信我，你会喜欢这场冒险之旅。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >多样法术</h2>蓝色的方块能量，当然有用武之地。冰、电、风、火等等，各种法术是你破解谜题的关键所在。<br>冰霜之力演示：<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2055620/extras/95d98e86704b2cc24c2879c124b31b49.poster.avif?t=1665541470\" width=640 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2055620/extras/95d98e86704b2cc24c2879c124b31b49.webm?t=1665541470\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2055620/extras/95d98e86704b2cc24c2879c124b31b49.mp4?t=1665541470\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>闪电之力演示：<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2055620/extras/eeb550c7bad8f30bda6258fcbf2f354c.poster.avif?t=1665541470\" width=640 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2055620/extras/eeb550c7bad8f30bda6258fcbf2f354c.webm?t=1665541470\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2055620/extras/eeb550c7bad8f30bda6258fcbf2f354c.mp4?t=1665541470\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>想象一下，是不是还有其他更多的法术等待你发现？<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >巨大谜题</h2>除了标准的房间俄罗斯方块谜题，当然得有大型的谜题。<br>大型谜题混合了多个房间，并且有更多的有趣机制，等你挑战。<br>比如，其中一种是双房间同步谜题，需要同时控制完成两个房间的方块达成挑战。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >最终一战</h2>面对位置的危险，当然可以使用战斗的手段获得胜利。不管是房间里还是野外，都有可能有怪物威胁你的生命。<br>是选择直面危险，还是避开，都取决于你的智慧。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >开放世界+俄罗斯发方块=？有答案了么? 加入心愿单，等待方块落下吧！</h2>",
